data.description: Welcome home to this country estate nestled in the serene beauty of Rome. This timeless traditional-style home offers a spacious floor plan with gleaming hardwood floors and high ceilings throughout the main level, evoking a sense of refined elegance and rustic charm. Sunlight streaming through the generous windows, casting a warm glow upon the stylish fixtures and finishes that grace every room. The bright and open family room beckons with a welcoming gas fireplace, inviting you to unwind in its cozy embrace while basking in the gentle radiance of natural light. The stylish kitchen is a culinary masterpiece, featuring beautiful white cabinetry, a captivating tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances, and quartz countertops with a breakfast bar. Enjoy a morning cup of coffee in the breakfast room, immersing yourself in the tranquility of the surrounding countryside. Off the kitchen area, you will find a spacious laundry room with cabinetry and a sink that adds a touch of practicality to your daily routine. The main floor is home to a luxurious primary suite, a haven of relaxation. Indulge in the elegant en-suite bath, boasting a sumptuous soaking tub, a large stand-up tile shower, and a walk-in closet that suites your every storage need. Step outside through a separate outdoor access and find solace on the front porch, taking in nature's enchanting sights and sounds. Upstairs, two additional bedrooms share a well-appointed hall bath, complete with a double vanity. You step down into the partially finished basement, where this home offers up even more possibilities. It's here that a large bonus room awaits your creative vision—transform it into a theater room, a game room, or a home office to perfectly complement your family's needs. A stubbed bath offers future customization opportunities, allowing you to expand this haven of refined country living. A two-car garage and a craftsman's dream workshop located in the basement provide ample space for storage and creative endeavors. As you step onto the darling rocking chair front porch, which gracefully wraps around the side of the house, immerse yourself in the idyllic country setting. The private front yard is enclosed by a charming fence, while a cozy fire pit beckons, inviting you to relax and savor enchanting evenings with loved ones. This exceptional property is ideally situated near local shopping and dining, allowing you to enjoy the conveniences of modern life while reveling in the peaceful ambiance of the countryside. Indulge in the enchantment of living in this elegant country estate, where comfort, style, and the natural beauty of the surroundings harmoniously coexist. Embrace the opportunity to make this extraordinary property your forever home.
